				<p>
          The MemberSHPE Committee is in charge of tracking membership status records, coordinating SHPE|UIUC's internal mentor program (PartnerSHPE), and organizing social activities. Our efforts promote a strong sense of familia and build lasting memories for our organization's members.
        </p>
        <p>
          A lot goes into planning a social and we need committee members to help. Besides thinking of new and creative socials we need to work around budgets and ensure preventative measures are in place for the saftey of the organization and its membership. Underage drinking is not acceptable at any SHPE|UIUC sponsored event and it is important that our socials conform to all of the University's policies. 
        </p>
